OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUK firms will have to      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdisclose climate impact    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Some large UK businesses will have to  
OL,6, start disclosing their environmental   
OL,7, impact, under new rules to be brought  
OL,8, in by the chancellor.                  
OL,10,FThe requirements will also apply to    
OL,11,Finvestment products and pension        
OL,12,Fschemes.                               
OL,14,FIt comes ahead of November's COP26     
OL,15,Fmeeting in Glasgow, where world leaders
OL,16,Fwill discuss their climate commitments.
OL,18,FExperts say the UK, which is hosting   
OL,19,Fthe event, is  not currently on track  
OL,20,Fto meet its own emissions targets.     
